# Open positions

We are currently looking for new group members with passion, talent, and grit! 

If you are interested in working with us as a PhD student or postdoc, please send an email to [Prof. Moin Qureshi](mailto:moin@gatech.edu). State briefly why you are interested and attach a CV, including information about the grades you had as an undergraduate. **<font color="red">Important</font>: please insert _"Application PhD"_ or _"Application Postdoc"_ in the subject line to indicate you have read through this website.**

If you are a Masters student at Georgia Tech looking for a Master project, contact Prof. Moin Qureshi or any group member via email or stop by the lab. If you are interested in pursuing a Masters degree at Georgia Tech, see [ECE Graduate Academics](https://www.ece.gatech.edu/academics/graduate-studies) and [ECE Graduate Admissions](https://www.ece.gatech.edu/graduate-admissions).


